@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fieqsa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = (tmp / 0.16)
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.36) + (wp.sin(v1 + 0.39) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.00)))
    v2 = wp.cos((0.98 - v0))
    v1 = (0.99 + ((tmp + 0.78 + v2 + 0.74) + v1))
    data[tid] = v0
